{
  "stem": "26731.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was quite-- I don't-- by the time you came back, half of the bucket was empty because you had to go down again and up.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Lo and behold, what happened, I was there and heard there's a bakery not-- down the street.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They might have some bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "OK, I'm going to go, and actually got some bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And suddenly, on the way back, I hear, hey, ho, stop!",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I look around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There were some Russian soldiers behind me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They wanted me to come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But in front of me, out of our building, our apartment house, some other Russians came and said-- more or less motioned-- let him go, we have him here.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there I was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And of course, right then, they didn't believe me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You are a Jew?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All Jews kaput!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All Jews.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I had to show actually my identification.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And actually, the front troops were very decent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What was your impression of the liberating Russian army?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the liberating-- I always have a soft spot for the Russians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, the main force came from the east, Mark-- Marshal Zhukov.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what I was being told, that already they got-- the SS got to the Jews in the north, rounding them up and killing them, or whether they did.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they didn't get to us because from the southern-- and Berlin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Marshal Konev, the one with a bald, shaven head, came in so fast.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't expect him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were surprised to see him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He just came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Germans, everybody, we knew they come from the east.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But now, there comes a second army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the second army-- one army came from the south-- and Konev.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When they came in time and hear him, the front troops were very good.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
